content.rendered:
Directed by Mozez Singh.

Written by Sumit Roy. Mozez Singh. Thani.

Cast Sarah Jane Dias(Amira (as Sarah-Jane Dias)) . Raaghavv Chanana(Surya Kapoor Sikand (as Raaghav Chanana)). Manish Chaudhari(Gurucharan Sikand (as Manish Chaudhary)). Abhimanyu Garg(Hafiz). Rajeev Gaursingh(H.P. Mehta). Preeti Gupta(Gurucharan’s friend). Meghna Malik(Mandira). Malkeet Rauni(Dilsher’s Father). Anita Shabdeesh(Dilsher’s mother (as Anita Shabdish)). Kunal Sharma(Yadav). Kunal Sharma(Yadav). Paras Sharma(Dhruv). Raj Sharma(Tulsiram). Raj Sharma(Tulsi Ram). Harmehroz Singh(Young Dilsher). Chittaranjan Tripathy(Ajmani).Umer . (0)

Languages Hindi. English. Punjabi.

Producers Guneet Dogra. Chandan Gill. Achin Jain. Varun Khokher. Kushagra Kulshrestha. Sandeep Leyzell. Guneet Monga. Harjit Singh Rai. Mohit Rastogi. Tarun Revoo. Ajay Sharma. Mozez Singh. Shaan Vyas.

Production Metamozez Entertainment.
